              Ignoring Engineer Recommendations
            </h4>
            <p class="text-red-800">
              If an engineer specifies 4-inch projection for water table issues, don't switch to bench 
              footing to save money. Structural failure costs far exceed initial savings.
            </p>
          </div>
          
